---
import Container from "./Container.astro"

---

<div id="features">
  <Container>
    <div class="md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2">
      
      <h2 class="my-8 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
        Industry specific solution customization
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Create personalized industry solutions based on the business characteristics of each industry to provide you with one-stop products and services.</p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mt-16 grid divide-x divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-700 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 text-gray-600 dark:border-gray-700 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:divide-y-0 xl:grid-cols-4"
    >
      <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <img
            src="https://img.icons8.com/?size=50&id=C7rky4cCpMoC&format=png"
            class="w-12"
            width="512"
            height="512"
            alt="burger illustration"
          />

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              FMCG & Durable Goods Sector
            </h5>
            <br />
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              The research domain encompassing fast-moving consumer goods and durable goods (FMCG&DCG) primarily addresses sectors like food and beverages, daily essentials, cosmetics, home appliances, retail, and travel. To enhance the relevance of our research and consulting services, our research department has established various specialized groups.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <img
            src="https://img.icons8.com/?size=120&id=FbD6Xv31Xv3c&format=png"
            class="w-12"
            width="512"
            height="512"
            alt="burger illustration"
          />

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              Health Care Sector
            </h5>
            <br /><br />
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              Shuxuan's Health Care specialized survey stands as a cornerstone of the company's global operations and has played a significant role in Shuxuan's expansion in China. In China, we have a seasoned team of professional consultants possessing extensive knowledge in prescription medications, medical devices, and healthcare policies.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <img
            src="https://img.icons8.com/?size=120&id=tLIz7zXYwGSP&format=png"
            class="w-12"
            width="512"
            height="512"
            alt="burger illustration"
          />

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              Automotive Sector
            </h5> <br /> <br />
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              Shuxuan offers year-round marketing support services to diverse companies operating in the automotive industry. With a wealth of experience in domestic and international field investigations, our team of seasoned researchers is well-equipped to provide your company with the most appropriate business solutions tailored to address the recent environmental changes within the automotive sector.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="group relative bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10"
      >
        <div
          class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8 transition duration-300 group-hover:bg-white dark:group-hover:bg-gray-800"
        >
          <img
            src="https://img.icons8.com/?size=120&id=112293&format=png"
            class="w-12"
            width="512"
            height="512"
            alt="burger illustration"
          />

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              Other Sectors
            </h5> <br /> <br />
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              We are well into the Information Age of the 21st century, witnessing transformations not only in China but also on a global scale. The evolution of the information society demands that all industries adapt to avoid becoming obsolete. With over 50 years of experience, Shuxuan has accumulated a wealth of data and expertise across various sectors.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>